<TEXT>
<P>
A showdown between milers Said Aouita and Marcus O'Sullivan was quashed when it 
was announced that Aouita would run 3,000 meters at Friday night's Meadowlands 
Invitational. 
</P>
<P>
According to Aouita, the decision was made by meet director Ray Lumpp. But 
Lumpp said that the decision had been Aouita's. 
</P>
<P>
