<HEADLINE>
<P>
VALLEY ROUNDUP: MATTHEWS EQUIPMENT ACQUIRED BY CAPTECH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Captech in Los Angeles has acquired Matthews Studio Equipment, based in 
Burbank, in exchange for 4.9 million shares of Captech common stock. 
</P>
<P>
For the year that ended Sept. 30, Matthews had net income of $223,000 on sales 
of $8.3 million. Matthews is a maker and supplier of grip lighting equipment 
for the film and television markets. 
</P>
